! Zen Mode Settings

Distraction-free writing environment.

!! Layout

|!Max width |<$edit-text tiddler="$:/config/codemirror-6/zen-mode/max-width" default="700px" tag="input" size="10"/> |
|!Font size |<$edit-text tiddler="$:/config/codemirror-6/zen-mode/font-size" default="1.1em" tag="input" size="10"/> |
|!Line height |<$edit-text tiddler="$:/config/codemirror-6/zen-mode/line-height" default="1.8" tag="input" size="10"/> |

!! Features

<$checkbox tiddler="$:/config/codemirror-6/zen-mode/typewriter" field="text" checked="yes" unchecked="no" default="no"> ''Typewriter mode'' — keep cursor vertically centered</$checkbox>

<$checkbox tiddler="$:/config/codemirror-6/zen-mode/show-stats" field="text" checked="yes" unchecked="no" default="yes"> ''Show statistics'' — word count, character count, reading time</$checkbox>

<$checkbox tiddler="$:/config/codemirror-6/zen-mode/exit-on-click" field="text" checked="yes" unchecked="no" default="no"> ''Click outside to exit'' — click the background to leave Zen Mode</$checkbox>

!! Focus Mode

Dim surrounding text to focus on what you're writing:

<$radio tiddler="$:/config/codemirror-6/zen-mode/focus-mode" value="none" default="none"> ''None'' — no dimming</$radio>

<$radio tiddler="$:/config/codemirror-6/zen-mode/focus-mode" value="line"> ''Line'' — highlight current line only</$radio>

<$radio tiddler="$:/config/codemirror-6/zen-mode/focus-mode" value="sentence"> ''Sentence'' — highlight current sentence</$radio>

<$radio tiddler="$:/config/codemirror-6/zen-mode/focus-mode" value="paragraph"> ''Paragraph'' — highlight current paragraph</$radio>

!! Keyboard Shortcut

Press ''Escape'' to exit Zen Mode at any time.

<$reveal type="nomatch" state="$:/state/codemirror-6/zen-mode" text="yes">
